examples.en: She chattered excitedly like a child.
The dog's tail began to wag excitedly.
The people were clotting into groups, chattering excitedly.
People had gathered and were talking excitedly.
They were all jumping up and down and screaming excitedly.
examples.ru: Все они подпрыгивали на месте и азартно кричали.

examples.en: Fans excitedly took snapshots of the rock star as he dashed into the hotel.
examples.ru: Поклонники радостно фотографировали звезду рок-музыки, когда тот прорывался в гостиницу.
